com.buschmais.jqassistant.core.store.impl

Class AbstractGraphStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.buschmais.jqassistant.core.store.impl.AbstractGraphStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Store
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmbeddedGraphStore, GraphDbStore

    public abstract class AbstractGraphStore
extends Object
implements Store
    Abstract base implementation of a Store.

    Provides methods for managing the life packages of a store, transactions, resolving descriptors and executing CYPHER queries.
